org.spongepowered.api.service.persistence

Interface DataSerializable

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    Banner, Banner.PatternLayer, Beacon, BrewingStand, Chest, CommandBlock, Comparator, DaylightDetector, Dispenser, Dropper, DyeColor, EnchantmentTable, EnderChest, EndPortal, EntitySnapshot, Furnace, Hopper, HorseColor, HorseStyle, HorseVariant, ItemStack, Lockable, MobSpawner, Note, OcelotType, Player, PotionEffect, RabbitType, Sign, SkeletonType, Skull, TileEntity, User

    public interface DataSerializable
    Represents an object that can be represented by a DataContainer.

    DataContainers received from toContainer() should be considered to be copies of the original data, and therefor, thread safe.
